Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还有什么东西忘记拿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当和水壶 零食都带好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君 小鸠 没有什么东西忘记带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的（两人）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样赤手空拳去远足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我去把包拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事啦


